questions.guidance_body:
## If you have multiple sponsor groups

This form collects information about one sponsor group. If you have multiple sponsor groups to report on, complete the form as many times as necessary.

To submit information about another sponsor group, go back your 'Collection requests', click into the form title, and add a new return.

## Saving progress and making changes

Your work will not save automatically. To make sure you do not lose anything, select "Save draft" regularly, and always before you go back or close your internet browser window.

If you need to edit or revisit any sections, select 'Back to contents'. You can edit your responses as many times as you like before you submit.

## Submitting your form

Once you have completed all sections, you can then submit the form. You will not be able to edit your responses once you have submitted the form.

## Get help

If you have questions about using Delta or need further support, [complete the service desk form](https://mhclgdigital.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/6/group/12).

## How we’ll use your information

Read how we’ll use the information from this form in our [link to privacy notice].
